From e88958cc15d722e0eb1660f5339e72b60d11bdca Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Etaash Mathamsetty
 <45927311+Etaash-mathamsetty@users.noreply.github.com>
Date: Mon, 27 Apr 2026 13:42:01 -0500
Subject: [PATCH 113/153] amdxc: Check for wmma support using vkd3d-proton.

Requires a pretty new vkd3d-proton.
---
 dlls/amdxc64/Makefile.in                |   1 +
 dlls/amdxc64/amdxc_interfaces.idl       |  22 ---
 dlls/amdxc64/main.c                     |  74 ++-------
 dlls/amdxc64/vkd3d_device_vkd3d_ext.idl | 193 ++++++++++++++++++++++++
 dlls/amdxc64/vkd3d_vk_includes.h        | 159 +++++++++++++++++++
 5 files changed, 365 insertions(+), 84 deletions(-)
 create mode 100644 dlls/amdxc64/vkd3d_device_vkd3d_ext.idl
 create mode 100644 dlls/amdxc64/vkd3d_vk_includes.h

